119
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:00,559
that must be enforced.

120
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,079
If there is fire

121
00:07:02,119 --> 00:07:03,399
burning the Huangquan Pass,

122
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,600
