325
00:17:06,650 --> 00:17:09,150
I want you to tell me the truth.

326
00:17:12,119 --> 00:17:13,199
Are you

327
00:17:13,199 --> 00:17:14,520
His Majesty’s Baixi?

328
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:20,325
Yes, or no?

329
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:22,680
Didn’t you just

330
