332
00:17:31,239 --> 00:17:31,920
Yes.

333
00:17:33,839 --> 00:17:35,319
I’m His Majesty’s Baixi.

334
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:51,200
Have you ever

335
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,720
