336
00:17:55,575 --> 00:17:59,254
Have you ever wanted
to get your freedom back

337
00:17:59,975 --> 00:18:01,534
and start a family?

338
00:18:15,025 --> 00:18:15,984
You have.

339
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:19,959
I can hear you saying

340
00:18:19,959 --> 00:18:21,719
