529
00:31:55,800 --> 00:31:57,050
and protect them in the dark

530
00:31:57,250 --> 00:31:58,530
just in case.

531
00:32:00,275 --> 00:32:01,800
And the maid,

532
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,400
