534
00:32:08,439 --> 00:32:10,119
Now you can rest assured?

535
00:32:11,675 --> 00:32:13,795
Thank you, Your Majesty.

536
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:21,686
I know.

537
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,560
You never

538
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,120
