560
00:33:45,975 --> 00:33:47,654
Since we will spend our lives together,

561
00:33:49,275 --> 00:33:51,200
all the things we can’t tell others,

562
00:33:52,079 --> 00:33:52,719
and all the things

563
00:33:53,119 --> 00:33:54,920
